node.text: Our dumb ass’ builds a $500 battery powered bike to race a $400k Lambo.... you’ll want to tune in IN ONE HOUR and watch season premier of Diesel Brothers on Discovery channel

node.title: $500 bike races a $400k Lambo, I’m In!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by The Muscle on July 17, 2021 tagging @inouyedesign, and @anchor_custom. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: I DREAMNT THIS UP 2 years ago, everyone told me not to do it, but I didn’t listen, i couldn’t listen it was stuck in my mind. I decided to build a house in the worst possible time in history... prices are crazy for material, material is hard to find, no one wants to work and I have felt like giving up 100x’s but.... it’s finally framed in and I feel a tiny bit of accomplishment. I’m not sure why this has tested my patience so much, and I swear to never build again, but I am stoked to finally be here. YOU HAVE A DREAM OR A GOAL YOU HAVE TO MAKE IT A REALITY.
